raw_text = "~ start
PlayerM: Naomiii 😩
PlayerM: I need your help
Naomi: What's up girl?
PlayerM: Okay don't laugh
Naomi: No promises 😂
PlayerM: I have a date today with my boyfriend and...
PlayerM: ...
Naomi: Spit it out girl 😂
PlayerM: I want to kiss him 👉👈
PlayerM: Like I REALLY want to kiss him
Naomi: Wait you've never kissed before? Not even with your boyfriend??
PlayerM: Is that weird??
Naomi: Not at all! Just surprising hehe
PlayerM: I've never kissed anyone before ever 🙈
PlayerM: HOW DO I DO IT 😭
Naomi: AWWW
Naomi: Okay okay first of all, relax 😊
Naomi: Honestly just don't overthink it
Naomi: When the moment feels right, lean in a little and make what you want sort of obvious
Naomi: img: naomi/16
Naomi: Like this
PlayerM: Okay I see
PlayerM: Let me try
PlayerM: img: mabel/104
PlayerM: Am I doing it right?
Naomi: Perfect!
PlayerM: But what if I mess it up on the spot??
Naomi: You won't! Trust me
Naomi: And if it's a little awkward that's actually cute
Naomi: Caleb bumped my nose our first time cause of how nervous he was 😂
PlayerM: LOL okay that makes me feel better
PlayerM: Thanks Naomi 🥺🩷
PlayerM: Gotta change quick, talk to you later!
Naomi: Go get him girl!! 💪
=> END
"
